  "religion": "Gellar is a non-devout Jew.",
  "politicalViews": "Gellar is a liberal Democrat.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.jweekly.com/article/full/30619/celebrity-jews/",
      "sourceTitle": "Celebrity Jews",
      "text": "Gellar is Jewish. Her mother and late father are Jewish, and word is, her mother is quite religious."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "In fact, take out her middle name and \"Sarah Gellar\" is a pretty Jewish name. The Jew celebrity devoutness-rating website, , gave Gellar a \"Jew\" score of 10 out of 15 because of the whole middle name deception. But that might not be the only reason."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Gellar has openly expressed her disregard for organized religion, saying:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001264/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Sarah Michelle Gellar – Biography",
      "text": "I don't believe in organized religion and I never have."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.marksfriggin.com/news99/3-1-99.htm",
      "sourceTitle": "Stern Show News",
      "text": "Furthermore, despite her mother's alleged religiosity, Gellar admitted to having Christmas trees growing up–but only because it was \"pretty.\""
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "I might go out on a limb and say \"Jew or Not Jew's\" rating was a bit high."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "Political dualism"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.wetpaint.com/network/gallery/surprising-celebrities-who-are-republican/photo/surprising-republicans-sarah-michelle-gellar",
      "sourceTitle": "Who Knew These Celebrities Were Republican?",
      "text": "Gellar's political affiliations are suspect. There are sources upon sources claiming that she is a registered Republican."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "One or two websites and I'd think it was a rumor, but given the sheer amount of people and organizations calling her a Republican, I'd have to say there's something behind it."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "However, the words out of Gellar's mouth point straight to liberal Democrat. For example, when asked about her thoughts on the 2008 election, (Obama's victory) she said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rU3NKpTJOCU",
      "sourceTitle": "Sarah Michelle Gellar thrilled over Obama win",
      "text": "I'm thrilled, I couldn't ask for anything better."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "And her thoughts on gay marriage are a far-cry from the standard Republican Party ideology. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001264/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Sarah Michelle Gellar – Biography",
      "text": "I have good friends, gay couples, who've been together for 18 years. It drives me crazy that in the eyes of the law, their love isn't acknowledged when I have girlfriends who have married four times by the age of 25."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "And she was not \"thrilled\" about 2008's passage of the California anti-gay marriage law, Prop 8. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rU3NKpTJOCU",
      "sourceTitle": "Sarah Michelle Gellar thrilled over Obama win",
      "text": "I think it's criminal, it's shameful."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "So, The Hollowverse will fly in the face of the numerous sites claiming Gellar is a Republican and declare her a liberal Democrat. Feel free to dispute in the comments."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
